            <h4>FAQs</h4>
            <h5>What is the Amtrak Vacation package cancellation policy? </h5>
            <p class="text-justify">Depending on the same package and the time of cancellation, cancellation procedures for Amtrak <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/vacation-packages.aspx">Vacations packages</a> can change. Before making a reservation, reviewing the specific cancellation policy for your package before making a reservation is crucial. A non-refundable deposit is typically required when booking a package. Should you need to cancel your trip, the refund amount will depend on how far in advance of your departure date the cancellation occurs. </p>
