            <p class="text-justify"><a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/amtrak/vacations.aspx">Amtrak Vacation packages</a> may be modified. However, this is dependent on availability and may result in additional costs. You can modify your package depending on the particular package and the date of the modification request. After making your reservation, contact Amtrak Vacations customer support if you need to change your package. They can assist you in determining whether changes are doable and any associated costs. </p>
